   <body>
      <context>
         <p>All the cabinets in the UPS system must be anchored to
the floor. Seismic anchoring is optional, unless required
by local regulations in seismic installation areas.</p>
         <note>Anchoring
bolts are not supplied. Use appropriate bolts for the floor type.</note>
      </context>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>Drill anchoring holes in the floor for each cabinet in
your UPS system.</p>
            <stepxmp>
               <table frame="none" outputclass="font:10" pgwide="1">
                  <tgroup cols="2">
                     <colspec colname="col1"/>
                     <colspec colname="col2"/>
                     <tbody>
                        <row>
                           <entry colsep="0">
                              <fig>
                                 <title>Anchoring Floor Hole Overview for 400 mm Wide Cabinet</title>
                                 <image href="../Images/Realitypxc10-80iec_general-normalanchoringoverview400_w85mm_0000241144.svg"
                                        placement="inline"/>
                              </fig>
                           </entry>
                           <entry>
                              <fig>
                                 <title>Anchoring Floor Hole Overview for 600 mm Wide Cabinet</title>
                                 <image href="../Images/Realitypxc10-80iec_general-normalanchoringoverview600_w85mm_0000241143.svg"
                                        placement="inline"/>
                              </fig>
                           </entry>
                        </row>
                     </tbody>
                  </tgroup>
               </table>
            </stepxmp>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Only for seismic anchoring: Drill seismic anchoring
holes (option) for the cabinets that will be installed on the left-most
and right-most side of the UPS system.</p>
            <stepxmp>
               <fig>
                  <title>Seismic Anchoring Floor Hole Overview for UPS System</title>
                  <image href="../Images/Realitypxc10-80iec_general-seismicoverview_w120mm_0000240984.svg"
                         placement="inline"/>
               </fig>
