                        </row>
                     </tbody>
                  </tgroup>
               </table>
            </stepxmp>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Mount each cabinet to the floor.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Only for seismic anchoring: Install the seismic
brackets on the left-most and right-most cabinets in the UPS system
with the provided screws and bolts.</p>
            <stepxmp>
               <fig>
                  <title>Front View</title>
                  <image href="../Images/Realitypxc_general-installseismicanchoroption_w170mm_0000235802.svg"
                         scope="local"
                         placement="inline"/>
               </fig>
            </stepxmp>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Only for seismic anchoring: Mount the seismic brackets
to the floor.</p>
         </li>
      </ol>
